Line1.8C8DF: To Hell and back, we have! In Tarsarak... mad fool, you wanted a guide to take you through the sandstorm.
Line7.8C8DF: To think you made it, following Meshif of all people. Maybe I should have taken the job... Seems it went better than this one.
VoiceDir1.8C8DF: Recognizing Player. Surprised, amused, yet still in pain.
